---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Services" description="Architectural digital solutions for Real Estate, Finance, and Staffing">
<main>
<section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 px-6 lg:px-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-full pointer-events-none">
<div class="absolute top-20 left-1/4 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-accent/5 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-blue-500/5 rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>
</div>
<div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl">
<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 mb-8">
<span class="flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
<span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent">Core Capabilities</span>
</div>
<h1 class="text-6xl lg:text-8xl font-black leading-[1.1] tracking-tighter text-white mb-8">Architectural <br><span class="text-gradient">Digital Solutions</span></h1>
<p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-12">We engineer high-performance infrastructures designed for scale, security, and technical prestige. Precision is not a goal; it is our foundation.</p>
</div>
</section>
<section class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto border-t border-slate-800/50">
<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16">
<div class="lg:col-span-5 lg:sticky lg:top-32 h-fit">
<h2 class="text-accent font-mono text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-6">Our Methodology</h2>
<h3 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight mb-8">Precision Engineered For Performance</h3>
<p class="text-lg text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-10">Our workflow is a rigorous architectural process. We construct robust digital ecosystems that leverage advanced technical frameworks to solve industry-specific challenges.</p>
<div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
<div class="flex items-start gap-4"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent">check_circle</span><div><h4 class="font-bold text-white uppercase text-sm tracking-widest">Structural Integrity</h4><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Built for 99.9% uptime and zero-latency performance.</p></div></div>
<div class="flex items-start gap-4"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent">check_circle</span><div><h4 class="font-bold text-white uppercase text-sm tracking-widest">Industry Specificity</h4><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Custom modules designed for Real Estate, Finance, and Staffing.</p></div></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-20">
<div class="relative pl-12 border-l border-slate-800">
<div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-accent accent-glow"></div>
<div class="mb-6 flex items-end justify-between"><span class="step-number">01</span><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent text-5xl opacity-50">domain</span></div>
<h4 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-4">Real Estate Ecosystems</h4>
<p class="text-lg text-text-muted mb-8">Our precision workflow begins with deep integration. For Real Estate, we architect PropTech platforms that synchronize global MLS data, automate lead nurturing via custom CRMs, and offer high-fidelity VR tour capabilities.</p>
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
<div class="p-4 glass-card rounded-xl"><span class="text-xs font-mono text-accent block mb-2">INTEGRATION</span><p class="text-sm text-white font-medium">Global MLS Sync</p></div>
<div class="p-4 glass-card rounded-xl"><span class="text-xs font-mono text-accent block mb-2">AUTOMATION</span><p class="text-sm text-white font-medium">Lead Nurture Loops</p></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="relative pl-12 border-l border-slate-800">
<div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-slate-800"></div>
<div class="mb-6 flex items-end justify-between"><span class="step-number">02</span><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent text-5xl opacity-50">account_balance</span></div>
<h4 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-4">Finance Architecture</h4>
<p class="text-lg text-text-muted mb-8">The second phase focuses on security and latency. We build financial dashboards designed for the modern quant. Our methodology ensures SOC-2 compliance and sub-50ms execution speeds.</p>
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
<div class="p-4 glass-card rounded-xl"><span class="text-xs font-mono text-accent block mb-2">PERFORMANCE</span><p class="text-sm text-white font-medium">Low-Latency API</p></div>
<div class="p-4 glass-card rounded-xl"><span class="text-xs font-mono text-accent block mb-2">SECURITY</span><p class="text-sm text-white font-medium">End-to-End Encryption</p></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="relative pl-12 border-l border-slate-800">
<div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-slate-800"></div>
<div class="mb-6 flex items-end justify-between"><span class="step-number">03</span><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent text-5xl opacity-50">group_work</span></div>
<h4 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-4">Staffing Portals</h4>
<p class="text-lg text-text-muted mb-8">Finalizing the solution with scalable infrastructure. Our high-volume ATS systems and candidate matching algorithms handle recruitment at scale, reducing friction between talent and opportunity.</p>
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
<div class="p-4 glass-card rounded-xl"><span class="text-xs font-mono text-accent block mb-2">SCALABILITY</span><p class="text-sm text-white font-medium">High-Volume ATS</p></div>
<div class="p-4 glass-card rounded-xl"><span class="text-xs font-mono text-accent block mb-2">LOGIC</span><p class="text-sm text-white font-medium">Matching Algorithms</p></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<div class="glass-card rounded-3xl overflow-hidden flex flex-col lg:flex-row">
<div class="lg:w-2/5 h-80 lg:h-auto bg-slate-800 relative">
<img alt="Tech Architecture" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-60 mix-blend-luminosity" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCQ9VtBWYUcRITGQNRChtYim4ITocx2YDpmn4dAswxgPRlGa3YKXPJvH9gSkkmXBIpvfNsCL4XmDzk0QAF1E0CkbJePGfQcjHgi76oPaipkJmPFBSqU0y8nDk_OIsKaH45HQzJqKb61bKLTx57C1HIyztBQNJw3obo27A5e4TR7vv1vgQBYSS3r81bVS2LMmxTem2-fOOneQJ3S53pJuTVRFnjSOSthwmgx6_RSBicj_zL7_6gdqWVc5gUsxoouos2NGnDQg4W-eD4" />
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-transparent"></div>
</div>
<div class="lg:w-3/5 p-12 lg:p-16 flex flex-col justify-center">
<div class="text-accent font-mono text-xs tracking-widest mb-6">IMPACT ANALYSIS 042</div>
<h3 class="text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-6">Driving 300% Scale Growth</h3>
<p class="text-text-muted text-lg mb-8 max-w-xl">By rebuilding legacy trading portals into microservices-based architectures, we reduced execution latency by 45ms and allowed for 3x simultaneous user scaling.</p>
<div class="flex gap-12">
<div><div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent">45ms</div><div class="text-[10px] font-bold text-text-muted uppercase tracking-widest">Latency Drop</div></div>
<div><div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent">300%</div><div class="text-[10px] font-bold text-text-muted uppercase tracking-widest">Cap Growth</div></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center">
<div class="p-12 lg:p-20 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-card-dark to-primary border border-slate-800 relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mr-20 -mt-20 w-64 h-64 bg-accent/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 -ml-20 -mb-20 w-64 h-64 bg-accent/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
<div class="relative z-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
<h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black mb-6 text-white">Ready for a Performance Upgrade?</h2>
<p class="text-xl text-text-muted mb-10 leading-relaxed">Join the elite league of digital-first enterprises. Let's architect your future together.</p>
<a href="/book-a-call" class="inline-block bg-accent text-primary px-10 py-5 rounded font-bold text-lg hover:scale-105 transition-transform accent-glow">Schedule Your Strategy Session</a>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>
</BaseLayout>
